My... Look, my daughter gave it to me for Father's Day.

1135
01:55:17,120 --> 01:55:20,038
我才不管是誰給你的，脫下來
I don't give a shit who gave it to you. Take it off.

1136
01:55:25,503 --> 01:55:27,879
克裏斯
Chris. Hey.

1137
01:55:29,966 --> 01:55:32,676
克裏斯，聽我說
Chris, listen to me.

1138
01:55:33,177 --> 01:55:37,055
奈特會來接你，帶你去他家
Nate's gonna pick you up. He's gonna take you to his place.

1139
01:55:38,558 --> 01:55:41,059
- 夏琳在哪？ - 我們得離開這裏
- Where's Charlene? - We gotta get out of here.

1140
01:55:41,227 --> 01:55:43,020
晚間新聞一直在播報我們
We're all over the 6:00 news.

1141
01:55:43,187 --> 01:55:46,523
- 我們得離開這裏 - 沒有她我不走
- We gotta get out of here. - I'm not going without her.

1142
01:55:46,691 --> 01:55:50,068
你考慮一下，我們在奈特家見
Think about that. I will meet you at Nate's.

1143
01:55:50,236 --> 01:55:51,361
你去哪裏？
Where are you going?

1144
01:55:51,529 --> 01:55:55,824
我得知道我們的逃走路線 是否也一同被洩漏了
I gotta find out if our out got spilled along with every other damn thing.

1145
01:55:56,075 --> 01:55:57,743
是誰告密的？
Who did it?

1146
01:55:58,578 --> 01:56:00,120
有誰沒參加？
Who wasn't there?

1147
01:56:01,122 --> 01:56:02,956
崔荷
Trejo.

1148
01:56:06,419 --> 01:56:07,586
奈特家見
I'll see you at Nate's.

1149
01:56:14,385 --> 01:56:16,803
- 是 - 你仍想要我嗎？
- Yeah. - Yeah. You still want me?

1150
01:56:18,139 --> 01:56:22,225
你馬上來這裏接我和多明尼克
You come down here right now and you get me. Dominick and me. Okay?

1151
01:56:22,393 --> 01:56:26,271
好的，寶貝，我兩小時候到，好嗎？
Okay, baby, okay. I'll be there in two hours, all right?

1152
01:56:26,439 --> 01:56:28,690
- 好嗎？ - 好
- Okay? - All right.

1153
01:56:30,276 --> 01:56:33,820
你真該死，克裏斯，你真該死
Goddamn you, Chris. Goddamn you.

1154
01:56:34,322 --> 01:56:38,241
- 你會坐飛機去洛杉磯 - 太好了
- You're on a plane for Los Angeles. - Great.

1155
01:57:25,998 --> 01:57:28,208
你為何這樣做？發生了什麼事？
Why'd you do it? What happened?

1156
01:57:29,711 --> 01:57:31,420
- 他們逼我的 - 誰？
- They made me. - Who?

1157
01:57:31,587 --> 01:57:33,338
安娜呢？
Where's Anna?

1158
01:57:33,840 --> 01:57:34,881
她死了
She's dead.

1159
01:57:38,094 --> 01:57:41,179
麥克和代替你的布裏登也死了
So is Michael and Breedan, the guy who stood in for you.

1160
01:57:41,681 --> 01:57:45,851
- 誰做的？是誰做的？ - 他們以安娜要挾
- Who did it? Who did it? - They had Anna, man.

1161
01:57:46,018 --> 01:57:47,769
是誰？
Who had her?

1162
01:57:48,521 --> 01:57:52,149
韋恩葛羅
Waingro.

1163
01:57:50,273 --> 01:57:52,150
韋恩葛羅

1164
01:57:52,400 --> 01:57:53,525
他一個人嗎？
On his own?

1165
01:57:55,361 --> 01:57:57,738
- 他替人··· - 誰？
- For someone. - Who?

1166
01:57:57,905 --> 01:58:00,240
他替另一個人工作
The other he worked for.

1167
01:58:02,160 --> 01:58:04,077
贊
Zant.

1168
01:58:06,247 --> 01:58:09,624
- 凡贊？ - 是
- Van Zant? - Yeah.

1169
01:58:09,792 --> 01:58:11,626
凡贊
Van Zant.

1170
01:58:11,794 --> 01:58:14,880
- 你確定嗎？ - 凡贊
- Are you sure? - Van Zant.

1171
01:58:16,758 --> 01:58:19,551
你有說出我們會怎樣逃走嗎？
Did you say anything about how we're getting out?

1172
01:58:20,178 --> 01:58:23,221
- 應該沒有，尼爾 - 快想
- I don't think so, Neil. - Come on.

1173
01:58:25,183 --> 01:58:26,808
我不記得，尼爾
I don't remember, Neil.

1174
01:58:32,315 --> 01:58:36,026
- 我去叫救護車 - 我撐不過去的
- I'll call a medic. - I'm not gonna make it.

1175
01:58:37,528 --> 01:58:40,572
我亳無感覺
I can't feel nothing.

1176
01:58:41,949 --> 01:58:44,868
我的安娜死了
My Anna's gone.

1177
01:58:46,037 --> 01:58:48,288
她死了
She's gone.

1178
01:58:49,707 --> 01:58:54,002
別這樣扔下我，尼爾，求求你，兄弟
Don't leave me like this, Neil. Please, holmes.

1179
01:58:55,338 --> 01:58:58,048
別這樣扔下我
Don't leave me like this.

1180
01:59:21,405 --> 01:59:23,615
- 是？ - 奈特
- Yeah? - Nate.

1181
01:59:24,242 --> 01:59:26,910
你用行動電話嗎？用普通電話
You on a cellular? Use a hard line.

1182
01:59:27,537 --> 01:59:28,703
這是新的電話
It's a new one.

1183
01:59:30,248 --> 01:59:33,041
他住在恩西諾區山景台
The guy lives on Hillside Terrace, Encino.

1184
01:59:33,209 --> 01:59:36,545
- 10725號 - 10725號，好
- 10725. - 10725, okay.

1185
01:59:36,712 --> 01:59:39,923
- 克裏斯呢？ - 他和我一起在我家中
- Chris? - He's with me, at my place.

1186
01:59:40,091 --> 01:59:42,425
接下來查出韋恩葛羅在哪，好嗎？
Next, Waingro, okay?

1187
01:59:44,554 --> 01:59:45,637
你有時間嗎？
You got the time?

1188
01:59:46,681 --> 01:59:49,975
我會抽空的，我要新的逃走路線
I'll make time, and I need a new out laid on.

1189
01:59:50,852 --> 01:59:52,102
你怎麼知道舊路線被洩漏了？
How do you know it's blown?

1190
01:59:53,771 --> 01:59:55,897
我怎麼能保證沒有呢？
How can I trust it?

1191
01:59:58,568 --> 02:00:00,443
好的
Okay, you got it.

1192
02:00:00,611 --> 02:00:02,654
保重
Stay healthy.

1193
02:00:07,743 --> 02:00:09,619
夏琳薛哈利斯
Charlene Shiherlis.

1194
02:00:10,371 --> 02:00:13,164
卓克在威尼斯區有地方可以讓她藏身
Drucker's got a safe house in Venice to stash her in.

1195
02:00:13,332 --> 02:00:16,543
尼爾的逃走方法 這裏處理完後，開始詢查
Our Neil's transportation. When we're done here, get on the phone.

1196
02:00:16,711 --> 02:00:19,254
有人正在替他安排
Somewhere, someone's trying to put it together for him.

1197
02:00:19,422 --> 02:00:21,798
你不認為麥考利已經有計劃？
You don't believe McCauley already had a getaway?

1198
02:00:21,966 --> 02:00:26,344
當然有，但他需要另一個計劃 要是你，你還會相信原先的計劃嗎？
Sure he did. Now he needs another one. Would you trust yours after this afternoon?

1199
02:00:27,388 --> 02:00:29,723
這告密的人，哪裏找到他的？
This rat motherfucker, where did we get him?

1200
02:00:29,891 --> 02:00:33,435
他是機密線人，通報搶劫銀行
He's a CI for a burglary cop. Called in the tip on the bank.

1201
02:00:33,603 --> 02:00:37,147
至於尼爾麥考利 我們還剩多少時間？
On Neil McCauley, how much time we got?

1202
02:00:37,315 --> 02:00:40,692
他有八到十小時安排新的逃走路線 之後就遠走高飛了
Eight, 10 hours for him to set up a new out. After that, he's gone.

1203
02:00:40,860 --> 02:00:42,819
拜拜啦
Bye-bye. Bam.

1204
02:01:35,665 --> 02:01:40,085
你向我們告發麥考利，你怎麼知道？ 是誰告訴你的
You ratted McCauley to us. How'd you know? Who told you?

1205
02:01:40,252 --> 02:01:42,879
誰告訴你的？你這告密者！
Who told you, you rat motherfucker?

1206
02:01:43,047 --> 02:01:44,673
是誰？
Who?

1207
02:02:12,576 --> 02:02:15,954
康納利針對墨菲 墨菲和萊格特一同對抗
Connelly back in for Murphy. Murphy with Leggat right there with him.

1208
02:02:16,122 --> 02:02:17,914
墨菲從網後準備出招
Murphy tees it up behind the net...

1209
02:02:22,086 --> 02:02:25,296
米勒跑到前頭，墨菲與裁判爭辯
...Miller out front. Now here's Murphy with the referee...

1210
02:02:28,884 --> 02:02:30,051
韋恩葛羅在哪裏？
Waingro, where is he?

1211
02:02:31,429 --> 02:02:33,680
- 他在哪裏？ - 我怎麼知道？
- Where is he? - How the hell would I know?

1212
02:02:59,457 --> 02:03:03,376
這裏有些什麼？
Well, what do we have here, hmm?

1213
02:03:03,836 --> 02:03:07,464
這裏漂亮嗎？漂亮
Isn't this pretty? It's pretty.

1214
02:03:09,925 --> 02:03:12,969
- 你這卑鄙小人 - 你告訴我你想脫離目前困境
- You slimy piece of shit. - You told me you wanted out from under.

1215
02:03:13,137 --> 02:03:16,306
你快嚇死了，對吧？ 你想脫身吧？這就是出路，夏琳
You're scared to death, right? You want out? This is out, Charlene.

1216
02:03:16,474 --> 02:03:20,143
- 你得到了什麼好處？ - 我···蠢女人
- Yeah, what's your end? - I... You stupid broad.

1217
02:03:20,311 --> 02:03:22,771
- 我怎麼會被牽連？ - 別衝動
- How'd I get into this? - Hey, hey, hey. Easy.

1218
02:03:22,938 --> 02:03:24,147
你聽到了
You heard me.

1219
02:03:24,315 --> 02:03:27,358
她飽受驚嚇，幫她倒杯酒
She had a rough ride. Why don't you fix her a drink or something?

1220
02:03:27,526 --> 02:03:30,528
- 去櫥櫃看看 - 去她的
- Look in the cabinet above the sink. - Fuck her.

1221
02:03:32,948 --> 02:03:36,076
- 你最好進了櫥櫃就不要出來 - 好，乖
- You'd better get in there and stay in there. - All right, all right.

1222
02:03:38,829 --> 02:03:41,081
聽著
Well, lookie here.

1223
02:03:42,249 --> 02:03:44,542
我叫卓克警探，洛杉磯警察局兇案組
My name is Sergeant Drucker, L.A.P.D. Homicide.

1224
02:03:44,710 --> 02:03:48,713
- 你要讓多明尼克在臥房睡嗎？ - 他和我一起
- You wanna put Dominick in the bedroom? - He stays with me.

1225
02:03:49,215 --> 02:03:51,132
來吧
There we go.

1226
02:03:58,724 --> 02:04:00,683
現在怎樣？
So, what now?

1227
02:04:02,937 --> 02:04:06,689
他說的對，你想脫身？這是出路
Well, he's right, because you want out, this is out.

1228
02:04:08,109 --> 02:04:11,986
- 你覺得你會出賣克裏斯 - 廢話
- You believe you have to betray Chris. - No shit.

1229
02:04:12,154 --> 02:04:15,115
對，你得這樣做
That's right. You would have to.

1230
02:04:15,282 --> 02:04:19,536
如果你不出賣克裏斯 多明尼克會是受害人
See, if you don't betray Chris, you victimize Dominick.

1231
02:04:20,037 --> 02:04:23,248
因為當你因從犯而入獄，他會變成孤兒
Because he becomes an orphan when you go to prison as an accessory...

1232
02:04:23,415 --> 02:04:25,875
你沒有父母可以照顧他
...because you got no living parents to take him.

1233
02:04:26,043 --> 02:04:30,421
他會被送去寄養家庭、少年感化院
So he ends up state-raised in foster homes, juvenile facilities.

1234
02:04:30,589 --> 02:04:32,841
之後他會偷車
Then he steals a car.

1235
02:04:33,092 --> 02:04:38,263
然後不斷入獄成為真正的罪犯
Then he winds up in gladiator academies like Chino and Tracy.

1236
02:04:38,430 --> 02:04:41,724
毀了一生
Fucked for life.

1237
02:04:41,892 --> 02:04:45,228
你是過來人，知道會有何下場
You know what happens, because you've been there.

1238
02:04:46,397 --> 02:04:51,568
多明尼克還沒機會選擇生活 但克裏斯有
Dominick didn't get a chance yet to choose his life, but Chris did.

1239
02:04:52,653 --> 02:04:56,239
你如果供出克裏斯，你不會有案底
If you give up Chris, you get off clean.

1240
02:04:56,407 --> 02:05:00,326
為孩子這樣做，你才能撫養他
You can do it for your kid, so you can raise him.

1241
02:05:04,498 --> 02:05:07,876
- 你還要推銷什麼東西？ - 各種東西
- What else are you selling? - All kinds of shit.

1242
02:05:08,752 --> 02:05:13,965
但我不用說服你，因為我是對的
But I don't have to sell this and you know it, because this kind of shit here sells itself.

1243
02:05:20,264 --> 02:05:22,265
好，丹尼，最新消息
Okay, Danny, here's an update.

1244
02:05:22,433 --> 02:05:25,768
- 卓克在二線 - 小隊長，等一下
- Drucker's on Line 2. - Lieutenant, hold on for a second.

1245
02:05:27,938 --> 02:05:30,064
小隊長，卓克在另一個電話線上
Lieutenant, I have Drucker on the other line.

1246
02:05:30,232 --> 02:05:31,608
三人通話吧
Oh, well, conference him in.

1247
02:05:33,110 --> 02:05:36,821
- 說吧 - 文森，是我
- Go ahead. - Vincent, it's me.

1248
02:05:38,741 --> 02:05:41,367
你的答案是什麼？
I want an answer. What's it gonna be?

1249
02:05:47,958 --> 02:05:50,460
我們準備好了，她會打電話
We're set here. She'll make the call.

1250
02:05:50,628 --> 02:05:53,796
好的，情況是這樣
Okay, that's good. Here's the deal here.

1251
02:05:53,964 --> 02:05:59,802
休班尼已經改過自新 成為洗心革面的好公民
Hugh Benny has reformed his wayward life and become a born-again good citizen.

1252
02:05:59,970 --> 02:06:04,515
顯然一個叫韋恩葛羅的牛仔 向我們出賣尼爾
Apparently, Neil got sold out to us by this cowboy named Waingro.

1253
02:06:04,683 --> 02:06:07,435
韋恩葛羅曾是尼爾的手下
Waingro used to be a part of Neil's crew...

1254
02:06:07,603 --> 02:06:11,189
後來替一個叫凡讚的洗錢人工作
...then he went to work for a money launderer named Van Zant.

1255
02:06:11,357 --> 02:06:17,153
小組正在凡贊家 因為他今晚較早前被殺
Units are at Van Zant's house as we speak because he got shot dead earlier tonight.

1256
02:06:17,488 --> 02:06:20,823
如果尼爾還有誰要對付 那就是韋恩葛羅
Now, if Neil goes after anybody else, it's gonna be Waingro.

1257
02:06:20,991 --> 02:06:24,327
韋恩葛羅入住機場馬奎斯酒店套房
Waingro just got himself a suite at the airport Marquis...

1258
02:06:24,495 --> 02:06:27,872
化名「詹姆森」，他現在在那
...under the name "Jameson". He's there now.

1259
02:06:28,040 --> 02:06:31,125
我要你把這消息告訴保釋人、組頭
I want you to get that to bail bondsmen, bookies...

1260
02:06:31,293 --> 02:06:34,504
警員及線人
...assignment officers and snitches in County.

1261
02:06:34,672 --> 02:06:37,048
任何可以把消息傳開的人
Anyone you can think of who'll put it on the street.

1262
02:06:37,216 --> 02:06:41,386
派人到酒店，並每隔半小時 親自收聽他們的無線電
Deploy a team at the hotel and personally check their come every 30 minutes.

1263
02:06:41,553 --> 02:06:45,640
因為也許尼爾會去找他，你感覺如何？
Because maybe Neil will go for him. Okay? How you feeling?

1264
02:06:46,350 --> 02:06:49,602
- 渾身是傷，但我會熬過 - 好
- Banged up, but I'll live. - Okay.

1265
02:06:56,986 --> 02:06:58,861
他在這裏
He's here.

1266
02:06:59,154 --> 02:07:01,364
尼爾還沒走
Neil is still here.

1267
02:07:01,907 --> 02:07:03,866
我可以感覺到
I can feel it.

1268
02:07:04,118 --> 02:07:06,661
但他會留多久？
But for how long?

1269
02:07:07,246 --> 02:07:10,164
最多七八個小時
Seven, eight hours, max.

1270
02:07:18,549 --> 02:07:19,882
你幹了什麼？
What did you do?

1271
02:07:20,592 --> 02:07:24,304
- 是你做的？ - 我沒做的比較重要，我不是賣金屬的
- That was you? - It's what I don't do, I don't sell metal.

1272
02:07:24,471 --> 02:07:27,390
原本計劃順利，你之後離開 但現在出了點麻煩
Would have been okay, you fly out after. Now it's jammed.

1273
02:07:27,558 --> 02:07:31,561
- 我們要一起走 - 那些和你一起的人呢？
- Now we gotta go together. - Those other people were with you?

1274
02:07:33,689 --> 02:07:35,815
我的朋友，麥克
My friend, Michael...

1275
02:07:36,900 --> 02:07:39,527
他知道冒的險有多大 他可以選擇不要參加
...he knew the risks. He didn't have to be there.

1276
02:07:43,532 --> 02:07:46,159
不入虎穴，焉得虎子
It rains, you get wet.

1277
02:07:48,203 --> 02:07:49,412
快收拾東西，我們離開
Get packed and let's go.

1278
02:07:56,587 --> 02:07:59,255
伊迪
Eady.

1279
02:07:58,256 --> 02:07:59,298
伊迪

1280
02:08:09,016 --> 02:08:12,268
你為何這樣對我？
Why did you do this to me?

1281
02:08:17,775 --> 02:08:19,817
你到底是誰？
Who are you?

1282
02:08:22,654 --> 02:08:25,782
會沒事的，你懂嗎？沒事的
It's gonna be all right. You understand? It'll be all right.

1283
02:08:30,662 --> 02:08:32,789
不會有事的
It's gonna be all right.

1284
02:08:33,791 --> 02:08:35,416
好
Right.

1285
02:08:44,009 --> 02:08:47,637
這地址D層18單位 有一輛雪佛蘭科邁羅
There's this Camaro at this address, Level D, Slot 18.

1286
02:08:52,351 --> 02:08:54,394
這裏有現金
Here's some cash.

1287
02:08:56,980 --> 02:08:58,147
這事什麼時候會結束？
When's it over?

1288
02:09:01,652 --> 02:09:03,194
22小時後
22 hours from now.

1289
02:09:03,654 --> 02:09:07,365
