- 是1735號房 - 謝謝
- 1735. - Thank you.

1451
02:30:16,759 --> 02:30:18,468
請注意
Your attention, please.

1452
02:30:18,636 --> 02:30:21,888
我們現在有火災警報
We are currently experiencing a fire alarm.

1453
02:30:22,056 --> 02:30:25,433
請不要驚慌，請不要乘坐電梯
Please do not panic. Please do not take the elevators.

1454
02:30:29,438 --> 02:30:32,065
- 該死 - 韋恩葛羅沒有動靜，我留在這
- Shit. - Waingro's not moving. I'm staying here.

1455
02:30:32,233 --> 02:30:35,819
我去查看樓梯，如果有煙，會叫你離開
I'm checking the stairs. If there's smoke, I'm pulling you out.

1456
02:30:40,116 --> 02:30:42,534
她父親呢？要我通知她父親嗎？
What about her dad? You want me to call him?

1457
02:30:43,536 --> 02:30:46,371
他在內華達山某處
He's somewhere in the Sierras.

1458
02:30:47,832 --> 02:30:49,999
而且她選了你
And she chose you.

1459
02:30:52,002 --> 02:30:54,379
選在你的房間自殺
She picked your place.

1460
02:30:55,923 --> 02:30:57,403
這種事不應該發生在她身上
It's not right, what happened to her.

1461
02:30:59,051 --> 02:31:00,385
是的，不應該
No, it's not.

1462
02:31:03,806 --> 02:31:05,849
是的
Ugh, okay.

1463
02:31:16,026 --> 02:31:18,153
有沒有辦法···
Is there any way...

1464
02:31:20,114 --> 02:31:22,615
能克服我們之間的問題？
...that it could work out between us?

1465
02:31:24,994 --> 02:31:27,579
我希望能說有
I wish I could say yes, you know.

1466
02:31:27,747 --> 02:31:31,040
可是終究···
But in the end...

1467
02:31:35,504 --> 02:31:37,672
像你說的
You know, it's like you said:

1468
02:31:40,384 --> 02:31:45,054
我一生全奉獻給被我追捕的罪犯
All I am, is what I'm going after.

1469
02:31:51,937 --> 02:31:54,856
我不是你想要的人，賈絲汀
I'm not what you want, Justine.

1470
02:32:05,326 --> 02:32:07,952
如果你需要走就走吧
Well, go on, if you have to.

1471
02:32:08,120 --> 02:32:09,704
不
No.

1472
02:32:09,997 --> 02:32:13,208
- 我可以留下來 - 我沒事，我可以應付
- I'll stay. - No, I'm okay. I can... I can handle this.

1473
02:32:16,378 --> 02:32:18,379
你自己小心
Just be careful.

1474
02:32:18,631 --> 02:32:21,382
打電話到這裏給我，讓我知道你沒事
Call me here. Let me know you're okay.

1475
02:32:22,301 --> 02:32:23,843
好嗎？
Okay?

1476
02:33:05,719 --> 02:33:06,761
走樓梯
Take the stairs.

1477
02:33:20,734 --> 02:33:21,776
誰？
Yeah?

1478
02:33:23,988 --> 02:33:28,157
酒店保全，三樓發生火警 各樓層的人都得疏散
Security. There's a fire on 3. We have to evacuate all the floors.

1479
02:33:28,325 --> 02:33:29,951
我不能離開
I can't leave here.

1480
02:33:38,836 --> 02:33:42,255
我們何不先談一下？
Why don't we just talk about this a bit, huh, brother?

1481
02:33:56,270 --> 02:33:57,312
他在17樓
He's here on 17.

1482
02:34:00,482 --> 02:34:02,817
看著我，看著我
Look at me. Look at me.

1483
02:34:06,155 --> 02:34:07,322
看著我
Look at me.

1484
02:34:39,229 --> 02:34:43,107
洛城警察，別動！手放在頭上！
L.A.P.D. Don't move. Put your hands on your head, now.

1485
02:35:18,227 --> 02:35:20,561
將我換到五號頻道
Switch me to TAC 5.

1486
02:35:20,729 --> 02:35:23,064
卡薩爾？ J J ？
Casals? JJ?

1487
02:35:23,983 --> 02:35:25,191
卓克，J J ？
Drucker, JJ?

1488
02:35:25,359 --> 02:35:27,902
文森，我在大廳的樓梯旁
I'm at the lobby level by the stairwell.

1489
02:35:28,070 --> 02:35:29,070
有什麼消息？
What have you got?

1490
02:35:29,238 --> 02:35:32,407
小組得乘坐其他的電梯去17樓
Teams are moving up the other elevators to the 17th floor elevators.

1491
02:35:32,574 --> 02:35:34,742
因為火警，電梯不能使用
All out of commission because of the fire alarm.

1492
02:35:34,910 --> 02:35:38,037
- 現場一團混亂 - 好，收到
- It's a mess. People everywhere. - Fine. 10-4.

1493
02:36:07,860 --> 02:36:09,444
趕快離開
Let's go, get out of the way.

1494
02:36:09,611 --> 02:36:11,529
不要擋路
Stay out of the way.

1495
02:36:19,455 --> 02:36:22,498
快，走那邊，好嗎？快點
Let's go. Go that way. We gotta go, all right? Go, go.

1496
02:36:25,627 --> 02:36:27,545
我知道了，長官
I got it, sir.

1497
02:36:29,673 --> 02:36:31,591
快點，快點
Come on, come on.

1498
02:36:37,431 --> 02:36:39,057
快走，先生
Come on, sir.

1499
02:36:43,312 --> 02:36:46,314
- 小心後面，女士們 - 我知道了
- Watch your backs, ladies. - I got it, I got it.

1500
02:36:48,984 --> 02:36:50,651
繼續走，夫人
Keep moving, ma'am.

1501
02:36:51,487 --> 02:36:52,570
走
Let's go.

1502
02:36:55,074 --> 02:36:56,324
繼續走
Come on, let's go.

1503
02:37:30,943 --> 02:37:32,610
走這邊，夫人
This way, ma'am.

1504
02:37:34,571 --> 02:37:36,364
後退，後退
Get back, get back.

1505
02:38:02,224 --> 02:38:04,642
- 把散彈鎗給我 - 是的，長官
- Let me have that shotgun. - Yes, sir.

1506
02:44:22,103 --> 02:44:24,855
我告訴過你，我不會回去坐牢的
Told you I'm never going back.

1507
02:44:28,193 --> 02:44:29,818
沒錯
Yeah.

1508
